overview: Chris Wheeler is Managing Director of award winning SEO agency Metalfrog Studios Limited. The business is based all around getting a return on your investment on optimisation. Chris has been developing and designing websites since 1997, and has been optimising since a year after Google was formed. Chris is an expert article writer and is a panellist on many SEO forums, work-groups and advisory bodies on the subject. There is a guarantee in place from Metalfrog which is that if your website does not reach the top page of the major search engines during the term of your contract, then you will receive their services free of charge until it does. This is a bold move, but one which works for Chris and his team.
